	<presentation id="index">
		<title>API Strategy Execution</title>
		<toc class="abstract">APIs are getting recognized as being strategic in many organizations, and yet there often isn't an explicit API strategy or program in place. As the API sector matures there are emerging patterns how to approach API strategies and programs within organizations. Depending on how far along on their API journey an organization is, there are various patterns and none of those are right or wrong, they just are different stages in the strategic use of APIs. We look at some of these patterns and will look at them in the context of API strategies and their execution.</toc>
		<date short="2023-10-25">October 25, 2023</date>
